trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser" /> objects.

A <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection?displayProperty=nameWithType> is returned from the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType> class.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection?displayProperty=nameWithType>从返回<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>，和<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType>类。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> objects returned by the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A> methods contain a snapshot of user information in the membership data store.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection>返回的对象<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.GetAllUsers%2A>， <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByName%2A>，和<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.FindUsersByEmail%2A>方法包含成员资格数据存储区中的用户信息的快照。

trans-unit.source: That is, changes to the membership user information in a <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> are not reflected in the membership data store.
trans-unit.target: 即，更改为中的成员资格用户信息<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection>不会反映在成员资格数据存储。

trans-unit.source: To modify membership user information in the membership data store, use the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType> class.
trans-unit.target: 若要修改成员资格数据存储区中的成员资格用户信息，请使用<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.UpdateUser%2A>，<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.CreateUser%2A>和<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership.DeleteUser%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.Security.Membership?displayProperty=nameWithType>类。

trans-unit.source: If you are not familiar with the membership features of ASP.NET, see [Introduction to Membership](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/79184d17-f4c7-4c9f-a073-cec4f5543980) before continuing.
trans-unit.target: 如果你不熟悉 ASP.NET 成员资格功能，请参阅[简介成员资格](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/79184d17-f4c7-4c9f-a073-cec4f5543980)才能继续。

trans-unit.source: For a list of other topics related to membership, see [Managing Users by Using Membership](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/824c3a24-f0af-427c-a652-0d2d1e9397cd).
trans-unit.target: 与成员资格相关的其他主题的列表，请参阅[使用成员资格管理用户](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/824c3a24-f0af-427c-a652-0d2d1e9397cd)。

trans-unit.source: Gets an enumerator that can iterate through the membership user collection.
An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEnumerator" /> for the entire <see cref="T:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection" />.
Enumerators only allow reading the data in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器只允许读取集合中的数据。

trans-unit.source: Enumerators cannot be used to modify the underlying collection.
trans-unit.target: 枚举器不能用于修改基础集合。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the membership user collection is thread safe.
Always <see langword="false" /> because thread-safe membership user collections are not supported.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method marks the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> as read-only so that <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> objects cannot be added to or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A>方法标记<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection>为只读，以便<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser>无法添加到对象，或将其从集合中移除。

trans-unit.source: Property values for the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> objects are not marked as read-only.
trans-unit.target: 属性值的<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser>对象未标记为只读。

trans-unit.source: That is, you can modify the property values of a <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser> in the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection> regardless of whether the collection has been marked as read-only by the <xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 也就是说，你可以修改的属性值<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUser>中<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection>集合是否已标记为只读的无论<xref:System.Web.Security.MembershipUserCollection.SetReadOnly%2A>方法。
